add database ==========

if it local paste to folder db  or use external
Admin > Data > AddSource  add database what u want  mysql oracle etc

<cfquery datasoutse="mydb" name="icanusesthisname">

SELECT user
FROM
people
</cfquery>


<cfdump var=#icanusesthisname#>

or

<cfoutput query="icanusesthisname">     > this query LOOPS results
#dfsf#
